  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"245\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCjEcGmQHMWbGaIiaPOaLOuiaxibMvLlSl1s5HgZLkiaXHIPB1xoU1Jib2osQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505175892\" data-ratio=\"0.42421875\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eb63aeeb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCjEcGmQHMWbGaIiaPOaLOuiaxibMvLlSl1s5HgZLkiaXHIPB1xoU1Jib2osQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-left:0;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-right:0;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn45h41xs3\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn45h4q0i\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：元宇</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-left:0;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn45h4rre\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">「</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">清仓」英伟达，孙正义对OpenAI约400亿美元的投资承诺已全部到位。而且，为了满足OpenAI对算力的巨大资金需求，这个投资周期也从原定的最长两年被压缩到了10个月左右。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn45h411il\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es31ac8\"><span leaf=\"\">400亿美元「弹药」已到位！</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3ffa\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">据知情人士透露，软银上周向OpenAI注入了一笔220亿至225亿美元的承诺投资。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es313i2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">今年2月，软银与OpenAI达成了一项总额约400亿美元的初步投资协议，其投前估值为2600亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.264\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1250\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1250\" data-height=\"330\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"148\" data-imgfileid=\"505175889\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3b8e2c2f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCsdXKZLwWOt2H5zNf1plNXoPPyMbibianYU9UsVyglRUgneWibbXcQetgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es31x3h\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这笔资金并非一次性到账，而是计划在未来12到24个月内分批投入。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3vcz\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">此前，软银已通过联合投资方式投入了约100亿美元，并直接投资了约80亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es312yf\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">最后一笔最大的注资在2025年12月的最后一周到账，标志着软银原计划总计约400亿美元的投资承诺已全部完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es37j0\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">据软银集团官方确认，其对OpenAI的最终投资总额达到了约410亿美元，这项投资使软银在该公司的股份增至约11%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3rrw\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">值得注意的是，这笔投资的完成速度比原计划要快很多，原定最长两年的投资周期被压缩到了10个月左右：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了满足OpenAI在算力、模型训练和产品扩张方面巨大的资金需求，整个注资过程被加速了。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjtnqtam1onr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3128b\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">OpenAI的身后不止站在软银。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjtnqtam1onr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3128b\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3128b\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtnqtac17ue\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;mjtnqtam1onr&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; font-family: mp-quote, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.034em; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;&quot;,&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mjtn4es3128b&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 15px;&quot;,&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mjtnqtac17ue&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">微软</span></span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtnqtac17ue\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">自2019年起就开始对OpenAI有过投资，外部统计其投资总额大约130亿美元左右。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es31x1c\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">本月早些时候又有报道称，OpenAI正在探讨接受来自亚马逊超过100亿美元的投资意向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.26627218934911245\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1014\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1014\" data-height=\"270\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"150\" data-imgfileid=\"505175888\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eae5135c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCVs36oUbmLJTcEw1fGd6GyXM8lQ0Veg3BhAGxtow2bL7X7ib38dJ4mDQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3zgg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">巨头环绕之中，OpenAI正变成一个巨大的AI算力竞争中心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3r8l\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">而微软、软银、亚马逊为它豪掷数百亿美元，正是为了争夺「下一代算力入口」，确保自己在未来算力竞争中的优势地位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">410亿美元花在哪里？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3v2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在投资界，孙正义就像一个永远在寻找下一个风口的「偏执狂」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5616666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1200\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"674\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505175891\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f70f9431&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYC2UItJ2U6ia9lGgekK7Yb8ib9W7YxRLz0pB2VElRObvNgCK2mCcu1oqUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:13px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn7lyt65z\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjtn7lz1ot5\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">软银集团创始人孙正义</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es382n\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">他从WeWork的惨痛失利中爬起，凭借着芯片设计公司Arm股价的惊天逆转，这位「投资狂人」再一次站上了牌桌。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3cwx\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在他这场高达千亿美元的AGI豪赌中，目前至少410亿美元已经注入了OpenAI，这些资金主要用于：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI重组：为更大规模的资本运作铺平道路，这项工作已于今年10月底完成；</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">支撑AI计算基础设施扩张：包括Stargate项目（目标到2029年投资5000亿美元于美国数据中心网络），以及与OpenAI合作的日本AI数据中心（2026年启动）；</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在全球范围内的相关收购与伙伴合作等。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es33i9\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">为什么软银会把钱砸到基础设施上？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es31kes\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">大模型每一次技术突破，以及AI应用的大规模应用，背后都离不开数据中心的算力支撑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es31604\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">如今，AI应用的兴起已经引发了对数据中心和连接解决方案的投资热潮。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es31604\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这波浪潮中，OpenAI也掉进了一个发展悖论：它的模型越强、用户越多、ChatGPT等应用越火，算力的缺口就越大。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3k6g\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">因此，这些钱更像是在给OpenAI的「AI底座」续命、扩容、加固。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3fbb\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">而对于软银来说，这410亿美元更像是一张昂贵的门票，为自己预定了未来在全球「算力供给链」中更核心的位置。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">万亿IPO叙事</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">需要资本「铺垫」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es318aw\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">今年10月底，OpenAI重组为「公益公司（Public Benefit Corporation,PBC）」，为其未来的融资和发展铺平道路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es318aw\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">此举也被广泛认为是为其最终进行IPO做准备。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es31jhv\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">据知情人士称，这次重组也为孙正义后续225亿美元的到位创造了条件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es31jhv\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">正是在这次重组之后，孙正义宣布了将于年底支付剩余225亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3m8v\">重组之后，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">OpenAI的IPO计划也反复被媒体曝光。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es31jk6\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">其估值也从软银敲定投资时的2600亿美元快速抬升：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">10月二级交易定价约5000亿美元。近期又有报道称其正洽谈新一轮融资，估值或讨论在约7500亿至最高8300亿美元区间，市场也出现其冲击万亿美元IPO估值的预期。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3p9n\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">支撑OpenAI近万亿IPO叙事的，除了其周活跃用户已经达到8亿的ChatGPT应用，超过100万家企业客户之外，还有OpenAI做出的未来几年超过1.4万亿美元的基础设施投资承诺。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es33h6\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">其中包括与英伟达、AMD和博通的协议。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3rs2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，这一切都需要资金的持续注入来托底。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">忍痛清仓英伟达背后</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es31lgh\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了履行400亿美元投资承诺，孙正义再次展现出惊人气魄，把自己手中最容易变现、最值钱的筹码，直接换成「新赌局」的筹码：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">清仓其在英伟达持有的全部58亿美元股份，加上其他现金来源，全部用来支持对OpenAI的投资计划。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3pfs\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">将这笔交易与软银近期的另一笔交易放在一起看，更像是同一张棋盘上的两步棋：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es31a6s\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">一边把英伟达58亿美元的持仓清掉，为OpenAI的巨额投资「补足弹药」。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3348\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">另一边同意斥资40亿美元收购数据中心投资公司DigitalBridge，「加强其在人工智能领域的布局」。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2636363636363636\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1100\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1100\" data-height=\"290\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"148\" data-imgfileid=\"505175890\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=52aa0af1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb14tKKLE6pVq7YVSJibxNhYCadozUjWIMh3vib5j2bdQQzvBHRa2eRf2hAicpHWwSueCYibVmhXCv4mXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3gfe\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">对比之下，孙正义在AI领域的布局也清晰显露出来：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">软银不只是押注「AI会涨」，而是还在把资金和资产配置，向「AI基础设施与入口」上倾斜。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es323x7\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">由此也能看出一种很「孙正义式」的杀伐决断：一旦做出承诺就不会再犹豫，敢于拿手中最优质的资产作为新的筹码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es323wm\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">多年来，软银一直大举押注科技和人工智能公司，并且是英伟达的早期投资者。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3ocs\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这次除了「清仓」英伟达，孙正义还进行了多项重大的投资组合调整，包括出售约91亿美元的T-Mobile股票，以Arm股份作为抵押</span>的保证金贷款<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">，以及大幅裁减其愿景基金团队人员等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn45h4x2e\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjtn4es3s5d\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">所有这些都是为了把旧的筹码置换出来，全部投向一场更大的赌局。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2025/12/30/softbank-openai-investment.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2025/12/30/softbank-openai-investment.html</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\">\n   <br>\n  </p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "软银已在 10 个月内向 OpenAI 注入 410 亿美元，远超原计划的速度，以满足其对 AI 算力的巨大需求，并预计将推动 OpenAI 达到万亿估值并加速 IPO 进程。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "软银已在 10 个月内向 OpenAI 注入 410 亿美元，远超原计划的速度，以满足其对 AI 算力的巨大需求，并预计将推动 OpenAI 达到万亿估值并加速 IPO 进程。",
  "summary": "新智元报道指出，软银创始人孙正义已将其对 OpenAI 的 400 亿美元投资承诺全部兑现，甚至最终投资额达到 410 亿美元，使其在 OpenAI 的持股增至 11%。这项投资在短短 10 个月内完成，比原计划的两年大幅提前，主要旨在满足 OpenAI 在算力、模型训练和产品扩张方面的巨额资金需求。这些资金将用于 OpenAI 重组、AI 计算基础设施扩张（如 Stargate 项目和日本 AI 数据中心）以及全球范围内的收购合作。文章强调，孙正义“清仓”英伟达等资产，是为了将资金集中投入到这场 AGI 豪赌中，抢占未来“算力供给链”的核心位置。微软、亚马逊等巨头也纷纷对 OpenAI 进行投资，共同争夺“下一代算力入口”。OpenAI 的估值持续攀升，从初期的 2600 亿美元上升至近期洽谈的 7500 亿至 8300 亿美元，市场预期其最终将冲击万亿估值并进行 IPO。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "软银已提前并超额完成对 OpenAI 的 410 亿美元投资，旨在满足其庞大的算力需求。",
      "explanation": "孙正义加速投资，反映了 OpenAI 对计算基础设施的紧迫需求，尤其体现在 Stargate 项目和日本 AI 数据中心等重大投入上，软银希望通过此举在全球算力供给链中占据核心地位。"
    },
    {
